{"tid":1276521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Google Account 知識普及] 用緊Android既人全部入黎!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-02T03:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:20:39.000Z","uid":142965,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5955321d12c665d90408a205617ce3057c7fd666","tid":1276521,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"Google Service原來可以比你紀錄同管理歷史位置 咁既話大家可以學識多一樣野去保護自己既私隱<br />\n<br />\n1. 去依個page 登入你有連繫手提電話既Google Account (如果你有多個account連手機 以下步驟就要遂個account做)<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/3118687?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Faccounts%2Fanswer%2F3118687%3Fhl%3Den&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=894d143a\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/3118687?hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 拉落去搵Delete Location History/刪除歷史位置<br />\n<br />\n3. Click &quot;Google Maps Timeline&quot;/ 時間軸<br />\n<br />\n4. 左手邊時間軸/Timeline 揀你想睇既日子 可以清楚見到咩時間喺咩位置<br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點</span></span> 左手邊紀錄部份 只移除部分位置紀錄既話 紀錄依然會喺地圖上出現 <br />\n但係toolbar度有個垃圾桶icon 可以移除當日紀錄 移除當日紀錄既話 全部紀錄同地圖顯示都會消失 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家千其唔好咁做</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600358ab76271d266195d4ce59160b2f5fc84e13","tid":1276521,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c3bc1ac1114d45705bff5b7ce995f44c5db45f1","tid":1276521,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9c48f798b48bb058615f79df2ab9ef01f72f4ec","tid":1276521,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl