0550","tid":1276521,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有另一樣!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n應用程式及網絡活動紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.google.com/maps/answer/3137804?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform=Desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fanswer%2F3137804%3Fhl%3Den%26co%3DGENIE.Platform%3DDesktop&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=d2370bab\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/maps/answer/3137804?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform=Desktop</a><br />\n<br />\n1. Click &quot;Web &amp; App Activity&quot;<br />\n<br />\n2. Click &quot;MANAGE ACTIVITY&quot;<br />\n<br />\n3. 拉落去搵日子<br />\n<br />\n同理 刪除全日資料先唔會留紀錄"},{"pid":"1e35645a7190fc44c4bba0d6c2119986a6e623a4","tid":1276521,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:55:59.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"67a32f2112c0924d0fef58f7cff23a77560c0f15","tid":1276521,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"35a743cd7475921a0c95742eaae2b8cf4ff6684d","tid":1276521,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"推"}]}